# Project Instructions For AI Assistants

This is an MVC-style FastAPI project generated by Fastango.

Use `uv` for all dependency and command execution:

- Install dependencies with `uv sync`.
- Run the API with `uv run fastapi dev app/main.py`.
- Run tests with `uv run pytest`.
- Run linting with `uv run ruff check .`.

## Project Layout

- `app/main.py`: FastAPI application setup and router registration.
- `app/api/routes/`: route modules.
- `app/api/deps.py`: reusable FastAPI dependencies.
- `app/core/`: settings, logging, security, database, and infrastructure helpers.
- `app/schemas/`: Pydantic request and response models.
- `app/services/`: business logic.
- `app/repositories/`: persistence access.
- `tests/`: pytest tests for generated behavior.

## Conventions

Do not read secrets directly from `os.environ`; add fields to `app/core/config.py`.
Keep route handlers thin. Put business rules in services and persistence code in repositories.

